            <title>[SPARK-29218] Increase `Show Additional Metrics` checkbox width in StagePage</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-29218</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Widths of checkboxes in StagePage are not proper and labels are wrapped. It looks weird.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;------&lt;br/&gt;
This happens always in two cases.&lt;br/&gt;
1. The default font size is big.&lt;br/&gt;
2. When the user increase font size.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve noticed this issue occurs to at least following environments.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Firefox 67.01 and 69.00 on Pop!_OS, an Ubuntu based OS 19.04.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Firefox 69.01 on Windows10.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Chrome&#160;77.0.3865.90 on Windows10.&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
